        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Calls for establishment of a Let's All Play Day to: (1) support the goals and ideals of Boundless Playgrounds; and (2) celebrate play as an essential factor in creating opportunities for children to develop physical, social, and cognitive skills.</p>]]></text>
